data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own this Newly Renovated 4 bedroom and 3 bath home on Oliver Point with views of Gunpowder River.  Designed in the Coastal Modern Farmhouse style the open living, kitchen and dining area is perfect for entertaining or relaxing with the family.  The Updated kitchen features high-quality stainless steel appliances, beautiful granite countertops and stylish fixtures.  Bask in the privacy of your 2nd floor Master Suite with 2 Large walk-in Closet and Master En-Suite.  The fully finished basement adds additional living space for 4th bedroom, office, playroom, yoga studio or guest room.   Community boat ramp just down the street with access to Gunpowder River.  And you are just minutes away from local hot spots like Bengies Drive-in (the largest screen in the USA), Gunpowder State Park/Beach or enjoying a meal with your toes in the sand at one of the many waterfront restaurants nearby.  With all new flooring, tile, carpet and paint you will feel like you are walking into a brand-new build but without the sticker shock.  This home is being sanitized regularly by the owner and ready for immediate move-in.  SCHEDULE your SHOWING TODAY!
